---
// CICDTools.astro — CI/CD tool comparison
---
<div class="cto-wrap">
  <h3 class="cto-title">Tool Landscape — 2026</h3>
  <div class="cto-table">
    <div class="cto-row cto-row--h"><span class="cto-c cto-c--n">Tool</span><span class="cto-c">Self-host</span><span class="cto-c">Config</span><span class="cto-c">Best For</span></div>
    <div class="cto-row cto-r1"><span class="cto-c cto-c--n"><span class="cto-d cto-d--amber"></span>GitHub Actions</span><span class="cto-c">Cloud</span><span class="cto-c">YAML</span><span class="cto-c">GitHub-native teams, OSS</span></div>
    <div class="cto-row cto-r2"><span class="cto-c cto-c--n"><span class="cto-d cto-d--cyan"></span>GitLab CI</span><span class="cto-c">Both</span><span class="cto-c">YAML</span><span class="cto-c">Self-hosted, all-in-one platform</span></div>
    <div class="cto-row cto-r3"><span class="cto-c cto-c--n"><span class="cto-d cto-d--green"></span>Dagger</span><span class="cto-c">Both</span><span class="cto-c">Code (Go/Python/TS)</span><span class="cto-c">Complex pipelines, local testing</span></div>
    <div class="cto-row cto-r4"><span class="cto-c cto-c--n"><span class="cto-d cto-d--purple"></span>ArgoCD</span><span class="cto-c">Self</span><span class="cto-c">Declarative YAML</span><span class="cto-c">K8s GitOps delivery</span></div>
    <div class="cto-row cto-r5"><span class="cto-c cto-c--n"><span class="cto-d cto-d--red"></span>Jenkins</span><span class="cto-c">Self</span><span class="cto-c">Groovy</span><span class="cto-c">Legacy, max flexibility</span></div>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .cto-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .cto-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .cto-table{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
  .cto-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:160px 60px 100px 1fr;gap:8px;align-items:center;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:8px}
  .cto-row--h{border-bottom:1px solid #334155;padding-bottom:10px;margin-bottom:4px}
  .cto-row--h .cto-c{color:#64748b;font-size:.6rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;font-weight:700}
  .cto-r1{background:rgba(245,158,11,.03)}.cto-r2{background:rgba(6,182,212,.03)}.cto-r3{background:rgba(74,222,128,.03)}.cto-r4{background:rgba(129,140,248,.03)}.cto-r5{background:rgba(248,113,113,.03)}
  .cto-row:not(.cto-row--h){opacity:0;animation:ctoIn .3s ease forwards}
  .cto-r1{animation-delay:.1s}.cto-r2{animation-delay:.15s}.cto-r3{animation-delay:.2s}.cto-r4{animation-delay:.25s}.cto-r5{animation-delay:.3s}
  @keyframes ctoIn{to{opacity:1}}
  .cto-c{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.7rem;font-family:monospace}.cto-c--n{color:#e2e8f0;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
  .cto-d{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}.cto-d--amber{background:#f59e0b}.cto-d--cyan{background:#06b6d4}.cto-d--green{background:#4ade80}.cto-d--purple{background:#818cf8}.cto-d--red{background:#f87171}
</style>
